# Server-side
<reply>
<data>
HTTP/1.1 401 Authorization Required swsclose
Server: Apache/1.3.27 (Darwin) PHP/4.1.2
WWW-Authenticate: Basic
WWW-Authenticate: Wild-and-crazy
WWW-Authenticate: NTLM
